sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant FE  as Frontend (React)
    participant GW  as gatewayserver
    participant PS  as paymentserver (PaymentService)
    participant SSE as PaymentSseService
    participant DB  as PostgreSQL
    participant CB  as CircuitBreaker (toss)
    participant Toss as Toss API
    participant OB  as payment_outbox
    participant DEB as Debezium
    participant K   as Kafka

    Note over FE,SSE: [Prerequisite] SSE subscription — connect before or simultaneously with confirm

    FE->>GW: GET /payments/orders/{orderId}/events
    GW->>PS: SSE subscribe request
    PS->>SSE: subscribe(orderId)
    SSE-->>FE: text/event-stream established<br/>(100ms keepalive heartbeat)

    Note over FE,K: [Main Flow] Toss payment confirmation

    FE->>GW: POST /payments/confirm<br/>{ paymentKey, orderId, amount }
    GW->>PS: confirm(request)

    rect rgb(220, 240, 255)
        Note over PS,DB: Phase 1 — short read TX (DB connection released immediately)
        PS->>DB: findByOrderId() + amount validation
        DB-->>PS: Payment (READY)
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 200)
        Note over PS,Toss: Phase 2 — no DB connection held, external API call
        PS->>CB: check call permission

        alt CB OPEN — failure rate >= 50% (sliding window 10 calls)
            CB-->>PS: CallNotPermittedException
            PS-->>GW: 503 Service Unavailable
            GW-->>FE: 503 (no SSE event)
        else CB CLOSED / HALF-OPEN
            PS->>Toss: POST /v1/payments/confirm (timeout 10s)<br/>with idempotencyKey header

            alt Toss approval success
                Toss-->>PS: TossPaymentResponse (DONE)
                rect rgb(220, 255, 220)
                    Note over PS,OB: Phase 3 — success write TX (@Version optimistic lock)
                    PS->>DB: payment.approve() + version check
                    PS->>OB: enqueue PaymentCompleted event
                end
                PS->>SSE: publishCompleted(payment)
                SSE-->>FE: payment-status event<br/>{ status: APPROVED, approvedAt }
                PS-->>GW: 200 PaymentResponse (APPROVED)
                GW-->>FE: 200 PaymentResponse

            else Toss error (4xx / 5xx)
                Toss-->>PS: WebClientResponseException
                rect rgb(255, 220, 220)
                    Note over PS,OB: Phase 3 — failure write TX
                    PS->>DB: payment.fail(errorCode, msg)
                    PS->>OB: enqueue PaymentFailed event
                end
                PS->>SSE: publishFailed(payment)
                SSE-->>FE: payment-status event<br/>{ status: FAILED, failureCode, failureMessage }
                PS-->>GW: 500 error
                GW-->>FE: 500 error

            else Reactor Timeout (exceeded 10s)
                Toss-->>PS: TimeoutException
                rect rgb(255, 220, 220)
                    Note over PS,OB: Phase 3 — timeout failure write TX
                    PS->>DB: payment.fail("TIMEOUT")
                    PS->>OB: enqueue PaymentFailed event
                end
                PS->>SSE: publishFailed(payment)
                SSE-->>FE: payment-status event<br/>{ status: FAILED, failureCode: TIMEOUT }
                PS-->>GW: 500 request timeout
                GW-->>FE: 500 request timeout
            end
        end
    end

    Note over OB,K: Debezium CDC — detects payment_outbox INSERT, publishes to Kafka
    DEB->>OB: CDC polling
    DEB->>K: PaymentCompleted / PaymentFailed topic published
